3. After 1k~3k steps of fine tuning on ether dreambooth (sks SPECIAL_TOKEN) or textual_inversion (<textual_inversion>), i got 2 customized model
4. I input the prompt of '$SPECIAL_TOKEN' + other odds and ends to try to draw the pictures of my item
